**Direct mutual fund plans** have no distributor commission, resulting in a 0.5–1.5% lower expense ratio than regular plans. While the difference seems small, compounded over 10–20 years, it results in a significantly larger corpus. This calculator shows the exact rupee cost of choosing a regular plan over a direct plan.
